article.description: — Blondeau Tchoukuiegno had a career-high 23 points as New Hampshire beat Maine 73-61 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Tchoukuiegno carries New Hampshire over Maine 73-61
article.linkText: Tchoukuiegno carries New Hampshire over Maine 73-61
article.story: DURHAM, N.H. -- — Blondeau Tchoukuiegno had a career-high 23 points as New Hampshire beat Maine 73-61 on Wednesday night. Tchoukuiegno hit 8 of 10 shots. Jayden Martinez had 17 points for New Hampshire (8-7, 3-3 America East Conference). Marco Foster added 14 points and Nick Guadarrama had 10 points and eight rebounds. Sam Ihekwoaba had 13 points for the Black Bears (4-14, 1-6). Vukasin Masic added 12 points and Kristians Feierbergs had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
